{"tid":1367601,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗夏日郊遊恩物—白花油！","createTime":"2019-07-26T10:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T17:07:22.000Z","uid":120631,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"67d83a7f768d70ac3ce61a9749ce8c5e12ab5505","tid":1367601,"uid":120631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:04:01.000Z","msg":"相信聽日好多巴絲都趁住星期六好天氣會入元朗郊遊<br />\n除咗基本野餐裝備之外<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望大家帶埋白花油喺身！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家都聽過搽白花油吹風扇會好撚柒涼㗎啦<br />\n的確白花油真係好涼陣陣<br />\n<br />\n如果入眼會點呢？<br />\n我前幾日就試過，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係會涼到10分鐘都開唔到眼嘅</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好清涼㗎<br />\n<br />\n如果大家想消下暑，不妨袋住枝白花油傍身呀<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">入落噴壺到更佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />噴一噴<br />\n涼哂！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望為大家帶來清涼嘅夏天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日元朗見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf98b87b7e9bcad29ee609a508e320583a3228a","tid":1367601,"uid":277186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:05:16.000Z","msg":"白電油定白花油好？ 燒野食驅蚊用"},{"pid":"bcfaa73bf330f26ea99600a21e7571d93efeedb6","tid":1367601,"uid":33887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:06:19.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講！"},{"pid":"51d7911946cbc08c17b1a5272d359e1093c1c38a","tid":1367601,"uid":123914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:07:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5e3d621cb44b4fa70794f52507674a3e39645afc","tid":1367601,"uid":123914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T10:07:22.000Z","msg":"it狗 你的